SVGMaskElementHeight.summary: The read-only height property of the interface returns an object containing the value of the {{SVGattr("height")}} attribute of the {{SVGElement("marker")}}.

blockquote.para: Note: Although this property is read-only, it is merely a container for two values you can modify, and .
